{"tid":2094772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獲眾議院外委會副主席點名稱讚的港人駐美遊說組織HKDC需要大家捐款！","createTime":"2020-07-05T03:06:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-07T01:15:46.000Z","uid":70063,"like":82,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"844bdf77ff8bb80cc7f1eee39b97e970b1e2ded4","tid":2094772,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:06:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=32&amp;v=W6Byt9dcG-k&amp;feature=emb_logo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Ftime_continue%3D32%26v%3DW6Byt9dcG-k%26feature%3Demb_logo&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=567f5fad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?time_continue=32&amp;v=W6Byt9dcG-k&amp;feature=emb_logo</a><br />\n<br />\n「HKDC」是為香港爭取高度自治和自由的民間外交使團，是第一也是唯一的在美港人駐華府的無黨派非牟利組織。<br />\n<br />\n隨著國安法來勢洶洶，香港籠罩在不見天日的黑暗之下，爭取民主人士將無法離境爭取國際聲援，其在國際社會發表的言論， 恐怕會帶來人身監禁、囹圄之災， 甚至被引渡至大陸境內。HKDC在華府的操作，今後更舉足輕重。<br />\n<br />\n為持續發展在美民間外交力量，HKDC需要您的長期支持。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>自去年九月成立以來，HKDC全力促成下列議程：</strong><br />\n<br />\n1.協助通過《香港人權與民主法》與《保護香港法》。<br />\n<br />\n2.堅持中國必須對侵蝕一國兩制及違反香港的高度自治負起責任, 促成國務院確認香港不再享有高度自治。<br />\n<br />\n3.對迫害香港自治與人權的相關中國官員實施簽證禁令。<br />\n<br />\n4.引薦14項香港相關法案，包含香港移民及難民保護法。<br />\n<br />\n5.透過上百場聽證會、簡報、會議、媒體文宣，使香港成為美國國會最受兩黨關注的議題之一 。<br />\n<br />\n6. 籌辦今年三月首場HKDC美港政策會議及遊說日。<br />\n<br />\n全數捐款將分配於：<br />\n<br />\n<strong>爭取美國儘快向香港人提供更強支援和保障 (40%)</strong><br />\n<br />\n-通過《香港空降法 》，《香港人自由與選擇法》，《香港高度自治法 》，與及建議及推動其他美國對香港的政策與法案<br />\n<br />\n-加強對侵害香港自治的中國與香港官員和機構實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n-每年一次舉辦HKDC美港政策會議及遊說日，提升三倍參加人數從75到225人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>提升在美政治影響力（30%)</strong><br />\n<br />\n- 加強就香港事務發言，成為香港事務的權威。<br />\n<br />\n-推動美國選民對香港的認知，就今年十一月大選進行「催票」活動。<br />\n<br />\n-遊說更多國會議員為香港發聲。<br />\n<br />\n-培訓額外10州或城市的在美香港人的草根組織。<br />\n<br />\n-與有志抗衡中共威脅和人權迫害的組織進行合作。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>拓展HKDC (30%)</strong><br />\n<br />\n-全職職員從1.5名增加至3名。<br />\n<br />\n-租賃辦公空間。<br />\n<br />\n-啟動華府獎學金計畫，資助美港相關議題和政策研究。<br />\n<br />\n全數捐款將用來資助HKDC，由執行總監朱牧民籌劃。<br />\n<br />\n所有捐款以美元結算。所有捐款者可以用匿名方式捐贈，HKDC並不會保存任何捐贈者在GoGetFunding 的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n捐款link：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkdc/?lang=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkdc%2F%3Flang%3Dzh&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=2a4b64fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkdc/?lang=zh</a>"},{"pid":"43e1f436dc9b7d27c548596dbf9bda267b600bfb","tid":2094772,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:07:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5da266940b269a80b0fbf50a12f1772d912224a2","tid":2094772,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e6a87936d3605d9d8f498cf94fbc589c990b19","tid":2094772,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:08:22.000Z","msg":"pish pish"},{"pid":"a3d09b2df73945dc9a64d71ed793b635d0b133ce","tid":2094772,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:08:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66dd9fa45b4cd1d5e97746956ae2726bea067e2f","tid":2094772,"uid":19557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"推 捐完再捐"},{"pid":"f82577c212e56e483c6ef179cdbc64acd6fe95ce","tid":2094772,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-05T03:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\"