度自治法 》，與及建議及推動其他美國對香港的政策與法案<br />\n<br />\n-加強對侵害香港自治的中國與香港官員和機構實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n-每年一次舉辦HKDC美港政策會議及遊說日，提升三倍參加人數從75到225人。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>提升在美政治影響力（30%)</strong><br />\n<br />\n- 加強就香港事務發言，成為香港事務的權威。<br />\n<br />\n-推動美國選民對香港的認知，就今年十一月大選進行「催票」活動。<br />\n<br />\n-遊說更多國會議員為香港發聲。<br />\n<br />\n-培訓額外10州或城市的在美香港人的草根組織。<br />\n<br />\n-與有志抗衡中共威脅和人權迫害的組織進行合作。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>拓展HKDC (30%)</strong><br />\n<br />\n-全職職員從1.5名增加至3名。<br />\n<br />\n-租賃辦公空間。<br />\n<br />\n-啟動華府獎學金計畫，資助美港相關議題和政策研究。<br />\n<br />\n全數捐款將用來資助HKDC，由執行總監朱牧民籌劃。<br />\n<br />\n所有捐款以美元結算。所有捐款者可以用匿名方式捐贈，HKDC並不會保存任何捐贈者在GoGetFunding 的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n捐款link：<a href=\"https://gogetfunding.com/hkdc/?lang=zh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgogetfunding.com%2Fhkdc%2F%3Flang%3Dzh&d=IQhlkTl0XfvqnQYO1cGwmiHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=2a4b64fc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gogetfunding.com/hkdc/?lang=zh</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:15:07.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe67d9e3f56843463ef1d1b4aff910e47f12ad3","tid":2094772,"uid":20727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11bb5981112c852a40bfbbb38648f41bd077ac07","tid":2094772,"uid":42884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:17:39.000Z","msg":"已捐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f90d7799e0892e89c6ad76993acc2a6c6d02a35","tid":2094772,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-06T00:18:41.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"c35ce78fcb3c1e631731586b8ca3529b263df28f","tid":2094772,"uid":18639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime